column5: After boating a nice fish last Sat. at my local Bass-hole, today I landed another good one! This is a  local water body I've fished since I was a kid and its been hurtin for many years due to over-fishing, so its nice to see it maybe rebounding!
Another park, another sunday..'Doobie Bros' Hey, a bass, wow!
nice looking largie, thanks for sharing with us.
Real nice bucket Pigeontroller  Thanks for sharing Leechman

Nice bucket! Looks like a spot my dad used to take me when I was a kid. He always told me stories of big bass there, but I don't remember us catching anything but catfish. Good to know he's not a liar, hahaha
